eplyTime":"2018-06-13T05:23:33.000Z","msg":"首先炎黃子孫係偽命題.華夏素來都不斷同唔同種族交雜,亦歷經多次大屠殺,現代所謂中國人其實大部份都係北方蒙古女真既後代,同炎黃一啲關係都無.<br />\n其次所謂炎黃子孫=中國人係用左西方民族主義世界觀,以前華夏既人係叫自己做唐人華人,並無民族觀念,更加唔會覺得華人就應該要整合係單一民族國家底下."},{"pid":"55f23cad83c6bf0898d323a28d1438c0cceab63d","tid":700054,"uid":150079,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T05:23:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔理你身處邊到，你呢家流緊既係炎黃子孫既血，請認清楚你既根係邊先</blockquote>中國人同華人兩個concept嚟</blockquote><br />\n台灣人，馬來人，新加坡同海外華人=華人<br />\n唔等於中國人<br />\n你啱，即使我有日本護照，我都係香港人，唔係中國人<br />\n如果九七前離開左既港人都冇特區護照，一樣係香港人，唔等於係中國人！"},{"pid":"6cf00465f2d91eda665c0f5faacacac3bc169bd0","tid":700054,"uid":150079,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T05:25:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇下基本法先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 搞笑</blockquote><br />\n你比中國洗哂腦"},{"pid":"22c1092ae094410289ec25c6cd6e66bab4eff722","tid":700054,"uid":171555,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T05:27:50.000Z","msg":"秦國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89b95c8e19d9fcbf5921aeae86883f923dd1adff","tid":700054,"uid":57012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"641bb47f6cb747cb7d3cb9d39c4e196637200d3d","tid":700054,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"c6ed87a45716a40e7f1e7b3983b475210a679310","tid":700054,"uid":150079,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T05:06:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>中華人民共和國香港特別行政區</blockquote><br />\n但係你係英國香港出身<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>我00後 回歸左啦</blockquote><br />\n00後特別多五毛，我夠98,唔覺得自己係中國人，根本係咩人係一個身份認同，香港淪陷咪就係你地呢d小蝗蟲，成個價值觀都有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <im